{"id": "22058", "post": "<div class=\"post-22058 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-adblocker tag-whitelist\" id=\"post-22058\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/please-consider-whitelisting-low-end-box-low-end-talk-from-your-ad-blockers/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Please consider whitelisting Low End Box &amp; Low End Talk from your Ad Blockers</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/adblocker/\" rel=\"tag\">adblocker</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/whitelist/\" rel=\"tag\">whitelist</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> April 17, 2020 @ 12:03 pm, by Jon Biloh</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/leb-banner-300x169.png.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/leb-banner-300x169.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a></p><p>We get it, it\u2019s 2020 and plenty of websites utilize terribly annoying and obtrusive ads on their websites. But that isn\u2019t the case here at Low End Box and Low End Talk, where we only have a few advertising areas, with only relevant advertisers (hosting companies, etc). We don\u2019t have any banner, Flash, animation, obnoxious sound, or popup ads. We do not implement these annoying types of ads!</p><p>From our data we know that many people utilize an ad block feature built into their web browsers which is preventing the page from fully loading.</p><p>We rely on the earnings from ads to operate Low End Box and Low End Talk, and all of it comes from our online advertising.</p><p><strong>Please add <a title=\"Low End Box\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lowendbox.com</a> and <a href=\"http://lowendtalk.com\">lowendtalk.com</a> to your ad blocking whitelist or disable your adblocking software.</strong></p><p>Thank you so much for your support and consideration. And most importantly, thank you for visiting our websites.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fplease-consider-whitelisting-low-end-box-low-end-talk-from-your-ad-blockers%2F&amp;t=Please%20consider%20whitelisting%20Low%20End%20Box%20%26%20Low%20End%20Talk%20from%20your%20Ad%20Blockers\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Please%20consider%20whitelisting%20Low%20End%20Box%20%26%20Low%20End%20Talk%20from%20your%20Ad%20Blockers&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fplease-consider-whitelisting-low-end-box-low-end-talk-from-your-ad-blockers%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/